Immigration policy benefits increased</h1>
</span></p>
<p align="justify" style="mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; text-justify: inter-ideograph;">
Work visa from the original 1 to 2 years (Vancouver, Toronto, Montreal work
permit to allow 1 year, 2 years in other regions) are extended to 3 years; do
not need to study the professional and work areas related to the abolition of
the company must be hired before Apply for a work visa. According to Canadian
immigration law, international students can earn a Canadian degree and can stay
in Canada for three years. In addition, the introduction of some provinces for
the student immigration policy has become a new temptation to nominate.</p>
